tidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Legislation_Year" atidlm:value="1999" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Revision_Number" atidlm:value="" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation>, and substituting the following subsection:</text>
