er" atidlm:value="" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of the principal Act</citation> is amended—</text>
              <label-para skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                  <text>By omitting the expression <amend.in><citation jurisdiction="nz">sections 11 and 12 of this Act</citation></amend.in>, and substituting the expression <amend.in><citation jurisdiction="nz">sections 13 and 14</citation></amend.in>; and</text>
                </para>
              </label-para>
              <label-para skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                  <text>By omitting the expression <amend.in><citation jurisdiction="nz">sections 13 to 27 of this Act</citation></amend.in>, and substituting the expression <amend.in><citation jurisdiction="nz">sections 15 to 27</citation></amend.in>.</text>
                </para>
              </label-para>
            </para>
          </subprov>
