e="Revision_Number" atidlm:value="" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of the principal Act</citation> is amended by omitting the word <amend.in>such</amend.in> in each place it appears.</text>
            </para>
          </subprov>
        </prov.body>
      </prov>
      <prov id="DLM49374" irdnumbering="no" skeleton="no" toc="yes" xml:lang="en-NZ">
